### ⚙️ Automated Tools (No-Code Options)
- **Octoparse**: Drag-and-drop interface, handles pagination, login, AJAX.  
- **ParseHub**: Good for complex sites with dynamic content.  
- Both allow exporting data into CSV/Excel/JSON without writing code.

