### 📑 Handling HTML Structure
- Learn to identify:
  - **Tags** (`<div>`, `<span>`, `<a>`)
  - **Attributes** (`class`, `id`, `href`)
  - **Nested elements** (parent-child relationships)
- Use browser dev tools (Inspect Element) to locate the exact HTML structure before writing extraction rules.

