### 🎯 Creating Custom Datasets
- Decide what you want: e.g., product prices, job listings, research articles.
- Build a scraper that:
  - Navigates pages (pagination, next buttons).
  - Extracts structured fields (title, price, date, link).
  - Cleans and saves data (CSV, JSON, database).
- Example: Scraping job postings
  ```python
  jobs = []
  for job in soup.select(".job-card"):
      title = job.select_one(".title").get_text(strip=True)
      company = job.select_one(".company").get_text(strip=True)
      jobs.append({"title": title, "company": company})
  ```

